Set up a pipeline that scales the values linearly between 0 and 1 and applies PCA such that 5 images from different wavelengths are combined to 1 channel data. (2 points)¶

In [6]:
my_pca_pipeline = Pipeline(
    steps = [
        ('scale', MinMaxScaler()), # scales data between 0 and 1
        ('pca', PCA(n_components = 1)) # Combines to 1 channel data
    ]
)
